    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points.",
